marc21:datafield.marc21:subfield: Alberto G. D'Atri's register of Modigliani paintings

Date based on latest recorded date in register (in column on ownership).
Register lists details about works by Modigliani in two page spreads, including: title, date of the work, where it was made, description, ownership, provenance, reproductions in publications, and exhibitions.
Archives of American Art, Smithsonian Institution
